data.description: Welcome to your dream home on Woodland Drive! This charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you enter, you are greeted by an inviting living room, bathed in natural light from the large sunroom windows that frame picturesque views of the surrounding neighborhood. The modern kitchen features sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and custom cabinets. Step outside to discover a private backyard oasis, perfect for entertaining or enjoying quiet moments surrounded by nature. Woodland Drive is know for its peaceful atmosphere and friendly community, creating a truly desirable living experience.
